e kern light small">Amanda Gefter</span></a></div><p class="h6 o6 mv1 pv025"><em>July 30, 2024</em></p></div><div class="post__title__meta flex flex-wrap flex-items-start"><div class="post__title__excerpt wysiwyg p italic mb1 mt025 pr2 o4 theme__text">Experiments that test physics and philosophy as “a single whole” may be our only route to surefire knowledge about the universe.</div><div class="post__title__actions h5 mt025 flex-auto flex flex-items-center"><div class="comments-button mr05 flex flex-items-center theme__accent"><a href="#comments" class="flex flex-items-center pangram"><svg viewBox="0 0 50 50" enable-background="new 0 0 50 50"><title>Comment</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M9.4 4.2h31.2c8.6 0 9.4 7 9.4 15.6s-.7 15.6-9.4 15.6h-2.2l-.9 9.4-18.8-9.4H9.4c-8.6 0-9.4-7-9.4-15.6S.7 4.2 9.4 4.2z"></path></svg><div><span class="comments-button__count ml075 small mbold disqus-comment-count" data-disqus-identifier="139377 https://www.quantamagazine.org/?p=139377"></span></div></a></div><span class="o-divider mh075 relative"></span><div class="relative"><button class="bookmark-button mh05 flex flex-items-center theme__accent-hover" aria-expanded="false"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 50 50" enable-background="new 0 0 50 50"><title>Save Article</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M2.1 0h45.8v50L25.5 37.5 2.1 50V0z"></path></svg></button><div class="q-tooltip hidden force-mobile-placement" style="width:130px;top:55px;margin-left:-65px"><div class="q-tooltip-content"><div class="q-tooltip-arrow"></div><div class="q-tooltip-inner" role="tooltip"><div class="h6t relative z1 uppercase kern--w mx025"><span class="small no-wrap">Read Later</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></section></div><figure class="lh-0 w-100P m-0_auto d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center flex-direction-column _p_last-of-type-mb-0 p-0 _19nesb1 _jrggmc _552kiq _14u1jsz"><div class="w-100P d-flex justify-content-center _1dby04b _q51w3l _10w8956 _1riapq9 image--module"><div class="w-100P max-width-100P max-height-100P mr-0p5em _last-of-type-m-0 _1sv5t9x _1q1eaf2 _pgs2sw _10w8956 component-img"><img alt="" src="https://d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net/uploads/2024/07/ExperimentalMetaphysics-crNicoRoper-Lede-scaled.webp" class="w-100P max-width-100P mb-1p5rem _194ln6i _14u1jsz _1sv5t9x border-none"/></div></div><figcaption class="d-block m-0_auto w-100P _ewzkgt _192y3bk _dc69mj"><section class="p-0_4rem _14u1jsz"><div class="max-width-560px w-100P m-0_auto d-flex flex-direction-column _1e0lyfy _k6y9ug _1ij7gf7 _1xqp4r2 _n5xvur _eugonq _l378w0 _19cu60 _14kcyqx _amwzaw _1re1wwt _pattribution-w-auto _46bwqc _pujp80 _pcaption-w-auto _1dxfdx3"><div class="attribution theme__anchors--solid wysiwyg pangram h6 mb1 fill-h"><p>Nico Roper/<em>Quanta Magazine</em></p>
</div></div></section></figcaption></figure><figure class="acf--code "><div class=""><div class=""><div class="acf-media"><div class="mha"><figure class="acf-media__inner mb2 relative"><div class="mha container--xs"><div class="hide-on-print"><style>
