<p>THE DIVIDING LINE between science and philosophy has never been clear. Often, it’s drawn along testability. Any science that deserves its name is said to be vulnerable to tests that can falsify it, while philosophy aims for pristine truths that hover somewhere beyond the grubby reach of experiment. So long as that distinction is in play, physicists believe they can get on with the messy business of “real science” and leave the philosophers in their armchairs, stroking their chins.</p>
<div id='component-66ad1bd5ca107' class=''><script type="text/template">{"type":"Image","id":"component-66ad1bd5ca107","data":{"id":139386,"src":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Portraits-in-circles.png","alt":"Black-and-white bust portrait of a man with a stern look, shaded eyeglasses, and short hair parted in the center.","class":"","width":990,"height":3690,"mobileSrc":{"ID":139434,"id":139434,"title":"Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE","filename":"Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE.png","filesize":1041540,"url":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE.png","link":"https:\/\/www.quantamagazine.org\/metaphysical-experiments-test-hidden-assumptions-about-reality-20240730\/portraits-in-circles-mobile\/","alt":"","author":"52094","description":"","caption":"","name":"portraits-in-circles-mobile","status":"inherit","uploaded_to":139377,"date":"2024-07-30 14:37:05","modified":"2024-07-30 14:37:05","menu_order":0,"mime_type":"image\/png","type":"image","subtype":"png","icon":"https:\/\/api.quantamagazine.org\/wp-includes\/images\/media\/default.png","width":1300,"height":1296,"sizes":{"thumbnail":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE-520x518.png","thumbnail-width":520,"thumbnail-height":518,"medium":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE.png","medium-width":1300,"medium-height":1296,"medium_large":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE-768x766.png","medium_large-width":768,"medium_large-height":766,"large":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE.png","large-width":1300,"large-height":1296,"1536x1536":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Portraits-in-circles-MOBILE.png","1536x1536-width":1300,"1536x1536-height":1296,"2048x2048":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/P