<p>With the two tied together in a Gordian knot, we might be tempted to throw up our hands, since we can’t put scientific statements to the test without dragging metaphysical statements along with them. But there’s a flipside to the story: It means that metaphysics is testable. That’s why Cavalcanti, who works at the very edges of quantum knowledge, doesn’t refer to himself as a physicist, or as a philosopher, but as an “experimental metaphysicist.”</p>
<div id='component-66ad1bd5d1f26' class=''><script type="text/template">{"type":"Image","id":"component-66ad1bd5d1f26","data":{"id":139388,"src":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise.png","alt":"","class":"","width":1400,"height":446,"mobileSrc":false,"zoomSrc":false,"mobileZoomSrc":false,"align":"align=\"inline\"","wrapper_width":"","caption":"","attribution":"","variant":"shortcode","size":"default","disableZoom":false,"disableMobileZoom":false,"srcImage":{"ID":139388,"id":139388,"title":"Section-2-noise","filename":"Section-2-noise.png","filesize":1744073,"url":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise.png","link":"https:\/\/www.quantamagazine.org\/metaphysical-experiments-test-hidden-assumptions-about-reality-20240730\/section-2-noise\/","alt":"","author":"52094","description":"","caption":"","name":"section-2-noise","status":"inherit","uploaded_to":139377,"date":"2024-07-29 19:07:37","modified":"2024-07-29 19:07:37","menu_order":0,"mime_type":"image\/png","type":"image","subtype":"png","icon":"https:\/\/api.quantamagazine.org\/wp-includes\/images\/media\/default.png","width":1400,"height":446,"sizes":{"thumbnail":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise-520x166.png","thumbnail-width":520,"thumbnail-height":166,"medium":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise.png","medium-width":1400,"medium-height":446,"medium_large":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise-768x245.png","medium_large-width":768,"medium_large-height":245,"large":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise.png","large-width":1400,"large-height":446,"1536x1536":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise.png","1536x1536-width":1400,"1536x1536-height":446,"2048x2048":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Section-2-noise.png","2048x